'''Eddy Munyaneza''' (yavutse 24 Ukwakira 1981) ni Umukinnyi wa firime mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]]<ref>https://artistsatriskconnection.org/story/eddy-munyaneza</ref> .  ''Munyaneza ufatwa nk'umwe mu bakora amafilime akomeye'' mu [[Burundi]], azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa documentaire zizwi cyane ''Le troisième vide'' na Lendemains.  Usibye gukora firime, ni umwanditsi, producer n'umwanditsi<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/51733_1</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 24 Ukwakira 1981 mu mudugudu muto wegereye umujyi wa Gitega mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]] <ref>https://neonrouge.com/fr/eddy-munyaneza</ref>.  Yarangije amashuri mu 2002. Nyuma yaje kurangiza icyiciro cya gatatu cya kaminuza muri sinema i Saint-Louis, muri [[Senegali]].<ref>https://www.indexoncensorship.org/2018/12/artist-in-exile-eddy-munyaneza-driven-to-become-the-man-behind-the-camera/</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2004 yabonye amahirwe yo gukorana na sosiyete yitwa 'Menya Média' aho yatoje ibijyanye no gutunganya amajwi n'amashusho. Muri 2009, yitabiriye nk'umukanishi muri filime ngufi ''Na Wewe'', iyobowe na Ivan Goldschmidt. Iyi filime yaje gutorwa muri Oscars mu 2011. 

Mu mwaka wa 2010, yasohoye filime ye ya mbere yerekana ''amateka ya Histoire d'une haine manquée'' <ref>https://www.afrique.fr/culturel/burundi-l%E2%80%99-histoire-d%E2%80%99une-haine-manquee-selon-eddy-munyaneza/</ref>. Iyi documentaire ivuga inkuru yukuntu barumuna be batutsi na we ubwe yakijijwe nabaturanyi babo b'Abahutu mugihe cya jenoside yo mu Burundi mu 1993 <ref>https://www.africanfilmdatabase.com/films/show/461</ref>. Filime yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Festival International du Cinéma et de l'Audiovisuel du Burundi (FESTICAB)<ref>https://africalia.be/fr/News-and-press/COPRODAC-advocacy-and-actions-for-training</ref>.  Muri uwo mwaka, yahawe igihembo cya Prix Spécial kubera uburenganzira bwa muntu mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican ya Ouagadougou (FESPACO)<ref>https://www.afrique.fr/culturel/burundi-l%E2%80%99-histoire-d%E2%80%99une-haine-manquee-selon-eddy-munyaneza/</ref>. Hagati aho, yahawe igihembo cy'ishimwe na perezida w'u Burundi, [[Petero Nkurunziza|Pierre Nkurunziza]], i Kirundo. Icyakora, yanenze perezida Nkurunziza kuba yarahataniraga manda ya gatatu.<ref>http://www.docmonde.org/en/lendemains-incertains/</ref>  

Muri 2016 yasohoye film ye ya kabiri ya documentaire, ''Le troisième vide''<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/48566_1</ref> .  Harimo amajwi y’imyivumbagatanyo ikaze y’imyaka ibiri ya guverinoma ya Nkurunziza aho abantu bari hagati ya 500 na 2000 bakorerwa iyicarubozo bakicwa, naho 400.000 bakajyanwa mu bunyage. Amaze gusohora filime, yakiriye telefoni itazwi akangishwa urupfu. Ni yo mpamvu yahunze igihugu mu mpera za 2016 maze atandukana n'umugore we n'abana batatu<ref>https://artistsatriskconnection.org/story/eddy-munyaneza</ref>. Icyakora, yasubiye mu [[Burundi]] muri Nyakanga 2016 no muri Mata 2017 kugira ngo abone andi mashusho ya ''videwo ya Le troisième'' . Nyuma yumwaka, film yahawe igihembo cyinyandiko nziza muri Guido Huysmans Young African Makers Award (YAFMA).<ref>https://afrikafilmfestival.be/awards/guido-huysmans-young-african-film-makers-award</ref>  

